snippet.title: 🏳️‍🌈 CONVERSION THERAPY & THE EX GAY MOVEMENT  🏳️‍🌈
snippet.description:
TW: conversion therapy, sexual abuse, physical abuse, spiritual abuse, homophobia. 

Today we talk about conversion therapy, a controversial and abusive practice that is still used on queer all over the world. 

Hi, I'm Jen, I am fascinated by the world of Christian Fundamentalism. On my channel I talk about different topics while doing my makeup poorly.

🔆🔆 MERCH! 🔆🔆
